Subject: ALSA: hda - Don't set invalid connection index in Realtek initialiaiton
Git-commit: 6a4f2ccb467e00281470cde2dee08fe5ecde62d1
Git-repo: git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/tiwai/sound-2.6.git
Patch-mainline: Submitted
References: bnc#591870

Skip initialization of connections of DAC widgets that aren't used,
which resulted in invalid verb parameters.

Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

